                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6123" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1543</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8649 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国民演绎竞合，能否共谱华章?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Can SOE and POE Achieve a Win-Win Situation  Through Co-opetition？ ——Risk Management Analysis Based on Company Z’s Cooperative Business Model of Operating Private Gas Stations</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘桂良，贺冰帆，刘瑶，李瑞琳，王苗，张锦欣，杨婷婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘桂良</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油化工集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石油工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国民合作；竞合博弈；经营模式；风险管理；他有我营；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Cross-Ownership Cooperation; Co-opetition Game; Business Model; Risk Management；Cooperative Business Model of &quot;Operating Private Gas Stations&quot;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为成品油销售的龙头企业，Z公司首创“他有我营”合作经营模式，以轻资产发展模式迅速提升其对成品油销售市场的占有率和控制力，民营加油站也因此获得金字招牌和规范管理，国民携手实现合作双赢。然而就在“他有我营”发展蒸蒸日上之际，营销管理、数质量管理等问题涌现，国民如何在竞合博弈中更好地实现共赢，又该如何应对新的合作经营模式所带来的风险挑战，是Z公司亟需思考的问题。本案例通过介绍Z公司“他有我营”这一国民合作实践，引导学员利用竞合理论分析国民的合作效应，并通过梳理Z公司针对“他有我营”的全面风险管理流程，应用理论解决实务问题。同时，“他有我营”是石化行业国民合作的创新尝试，以此为出发点启发学员思考未来国民合作的趋势，展望未来国民合作的创新模式，探究如何控制风险以保障高质量的国民合作，促进国民携手发展，共谱华章！</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a leading enterprise in the refined oil, Company Z innovatively proposed a cooperative business model of &quot;Operating Private Gas Stations&quot;, and rapidly  enhanced its market share and control over the refined oil sales market with the light-asset development mode. The private gas stations have also obtained brand advantage and standardized management. Thus, state-owned enterprise(SOE) and privately owned enterprise(POE) can work together to achieve a win-win cooperation. However, with the development of &quot;Operating Private Gas Stations&quot;, Company Z is facing some problems like marketing management, quantity and quality management and so on. It needs to think about how to achieve win-win in the game, and how to deal with the coming risks and challenges under the new cooperative business model. This case introduces the practice of &quot;Operating Private Gas Stations&quot; cooperative business model of company Z, and guides students to use the Co-opetition Theory to think about the cooperation effect of the SOE and the POE. Meanwhile, &quot;Operating Private Gas Stations&quot; is an innovative attempt of cross-ownership cooperation in the petrochemical industry. This inspires students to consider the trend of cross-ownership cooperation in the future, and guides them to imagine the future innovative models and potential risks and how to control risks to ensure high-quality cross-ownership cooperation, promoting the development of SOE and POE!</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司战略与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">竞合理论；成本效益原则；全面风险管理；风险识别；风险评估；内控“三化”理论；国有企业发展理论；民营企业发展理论；规模效应与协同效应</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
